            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="background-color: #b8484d; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0; color: white;">每月染髮新客UP</p>
                    <h3 class="counter" data-target="453" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0; color: white;">0</h3>
